"It looks like you've just changed a linked tag. To manually trigger "
"automated enrollments, run a <em>Resync tags for every user</em> operation "
"from the <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"%1$s\">WP Fusion settings page</a>. "
"Any user with the <strong>%2$s</strong> tag will be enrolled. Any user "
"without the <strong>%2$s</strong> tag will be unenrolled."
