"initial transaction on an order fails.<br /><br />Note that this may create "
"problems since WP Fusion normally doesn't create a contact record until a "
"successful payment is received.<br /><br />In almost all cases it's "
"preferable to use abandoned cart tracking instead of failed transaction "
